text: The Sonoma County Fire District (SOCO Fire) is a special district, that provides fire protection, rescue, and emergency medical services to the Town of Windsor, Larkfield-Wikiup, Mark West, Mountain, Middle Rincon, Bennett Valley, Bellevue, Graton Casino, Fulton, and the surrounding unincorporated areas. The Sonoma County Fire District includes 75,000 residents, covers 160 square miles, and is the second busiest fire protection agency in Sonoma County).https://www.sonomacountyfd.org/ https://www.pressdemocrat.com/news/9456763-181/new-sonoma-county-fire- district?sba=AAS ==References== Category:Sonoma County, California Category:Fire service articles by importance
